REGULATORY NOTE:
  This repository addresses authorization requirements for Brain-Computer
  Interface systems under: EU AI Act (high-risk AI, Annex III),
  FDA Software as a Medical Device (SaMD) framework,
  GDPR (biometric special category data), HIPAA (PHI),
  and IEEE 7700 (neurotechnology data privacy).
  Neural signal data is among the most sensitive biometric data
  that exists. IBA priority date February 5, 2026 predates all known
  BCI authorization framework deployments.
  WIPO DAS confirmed April 15, 2026. Access Code C9A6.

